{"tid":1624241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一圖話你知黑警冇可能變白","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T05:08:27.000Z","uid":186074,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ba66cc6f18a2c6077b556884a327fa827b8115af","tid":1624241,"uid":186074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5NHbLYG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5NHbLYG.jpg&h=7a58361a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔係話膠喉變水喉通咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n直頭要扮示威者搞裝修<br />\n<br />\n仲有期望良心警變白<br />\n<br />\n或者覺得佢地為自己權力而戰實在太天真<br />\n<br />\n根本成場show就係政治任務  中共最高指導人派武警落黎鎮壓 抹黑呢場運動<br />\n<br />\n到呢一刻  仲有政治潔癖既好好反思下  係咪要搞分化   搞割席?<br />\n<br />\n得罪講句  手足明明爆緊360    無啦啦有一批係隔離爆金鋪    最後記招又係入示威者數<br />\n咁係咪咩都唔好做?而家有蒙面法  你連戴口罩去商場唱歌既人權自由都被剝奪  <br />\n<br />\n所以  無論前線做咩   不危害人命<br />\n都絕對支持<br />\n<br />\n不完美 可接受<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"6a528a3dfd6934fae982a5170673a2728d598198","tid":1624241,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:19:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d4aac8b976011c632d8dc2b32d3fe69d0d510d2","tid":1624241,"uid":143382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:20:16.000Z","msg":"有冇片？"},{"pid":"4329ac2b2ffdc7a79e3eb1274a7324add58340e6","tid":1624241,"uid":186074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vcxCG7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvcxCG7g.jpg&h=75de6a3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d49aa68be02da452e2445b810e82343dcff59f5a","tid":1624241,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:54:53.000Z","msg":"Real?"},{"pid":"dc9e6041ba51690b04751e2386e18db0fb1fe69d","tid":1624241,"uid":272292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:59:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"090de2332f039563083e1e9a34474e96916a80